values: Last night was Homecoming for everybody at my skewl. Nobody asked me, but my bud Brian Hoyer and I hung out w/ a big group of seniors. We went to Soup Plantation, then to Ashley's house .. then we all drove to Elephant forest/ Quest Haven (which is supposed to be haunted and really scary). I had never been before.  And by the end of the night, I was too tired to go to the jaquzzi w/ Brian :( .It was like... 2 am!![Next time Brian ;)] But i had alotta fun. I met alot of new faces. that was my homecoming... how was everybody elses??

Hummmm... Im trying to decide weather or not I should dress up for 80s day tomorrow. I dont have leg warmers or anything really 80s. And what I do have, Im embarassed to wear!! I dunno. Tonight is youth group at 7pm... ill see yall there. Im going to Emmanuel Faith this time. Im giving it one more shot. Today i got in the power source for my computer. So i will be able to have my own up and running very shortly. Its gonna be nice. My mom JUST called on her cell and said "Me and Wayne are gonna go to the mall. He needs pants." What about me??!! What about my needs??!! "We'll deal w/ you someother day" she says. I luv u too Mom.

Its Tuesday (Oct 8th) and this is my first journal entry. Last night i went to an open call at this modeling agency called Trans Continental Talent. aka TCT. But i ultimatly decided not to sign w/ them. I dont want to do modeling. I would rather do commercials, television, and movies. Plus... I cant travel all over the US for a gig. So no. But oh well. The search for a good agent in LA begins... this weekend. This Saturday is going to sux the big one... I can tell. I have the SAT (the real deal) at 8am. Im going to die. ugh. Today Mrs. Randels (Gov/Econ teacher) made Alexis cry. And she said shut-up to the class like 6 times. She had something major stuck up her butt. And my ex (DesForges) embarassed the hell out of me today. I was leaving skewll 5th period and he said "What are u doing after school" and i said "ummm... watching a meiosis video"... it was not true of course. Its just a joke from Physiology class. Plus, I thought he didnt know what meiosis is. and he yells "Ur gonna watch a porn!! Hell yea. Im there" . So embarassing. i could have died. Everyone was lookin at me. ugh... i could just kill that kid sometimes. But what are Ex-boyfriends for n/e wayz. I know i should be more careful about who i date... but i have a problem with rushing into things. I get all emotionally attached before i know what hit me. I guess thats every girl to an extent. someone is IMing me. g2g. late
